    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台商家套利细则》及其相关规则的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1239487186232020992",
    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台商家套利细则》及《<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">京东开放平台商家违规管理总则</span>》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年5月14日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年5月20日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年5月21日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：补充商家套利中的&ldquo;商家&rdquo;定义，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">修订内容如下：</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">1、《京东开放平台商家套利细则》 </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: red; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: red; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家套利：指商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家套利：指商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: yellow;\">本规则所称商家，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构；商家应保证其关联机构同样遵守平台规则的约定，商家对其关联机构的行为造成的一切后果承担连带保证责任。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>2、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">《<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">京东开放平台商家违规管理总则</span>》</span></span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: red; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: red; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第七类 交易作弊</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">22</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【商家套利】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。京东有权视违规程度采取包括但不限于扣除违约金、延迟结算、剔除商家优惠券、京豆、红包使用资格、关闭/停用价保等权益、关闭/停用工具、商品下架、全店限售、钱包冻结、限制服务市场交易、店铺清退等处理措施。同时，京东有权追缴套券套利款项。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 207.4pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"277\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第七类 交易作弊</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">22</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【商家套利】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。京东有权视违规程度采取包括但不限于扣除违约金、延迟结算、剔除商家优惠券、京豆、红包使用资格、关闭/停用价保等权益、关闭/停用工具、商品下架、全店限售、钱包冻结、限制服务市场交易、店铺清退等处理措施。同时，京东有权追缴套券套利款项。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: yellow;\">本规则所称商家，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构；商家应保证其关联机构同样遵守平台规则的约定，商家对其关联机构的行为造成的一切后果承担连带保证责任。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
